title: Grateful Dead Live at Community War Memorial Auditorium on 1982-04-09
lineage: Cassette > Digitized 24/48 > Sound Forge 7 > CD Wave > Flac 16
description:
Set 1

Alabama Getaway-> Greatest Story Ever Told, Dire Wolf-> CC Rider, Bird Song, It's All Over Now, Loser, Minglewood Blues, China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider

Set 2

Women Are Smarter, To Lay Me Down, Lost Sailor-> Saint Of Circumstance-> Drums-> The Other One-> Stella Blue-> Goin' Down The Road Feelin' Bad-> Satisfaction, E: Brokedown Palace

reviews.review_text: Best sounding version. This is the best sounding of the available sources. Great sound actually, at a very good sounding venue. The performance is also quite good.
great memory I was at this show and have lost the scratchy audience tape I had....so grateful to be taken back via this fine recording of a fine show!
